The paper deals with autonomous driving, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) for obstacle detection and avoidance, and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for decision making. The use of Model Predictive Control (MPC) also falls under control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG) as it involves optimization and prediction.
